OL,3,CSenior police officer accused of
OL,4,C'double-jobbing' could face fraud
OL,5,Ccharges
OL,7,FBack in March after a query from UTV,
OL,8,Fthe PSNI confirmed a senior police
OL,9,Fofficer was at the centre of a
OL,10,Fmisconduct investigation.
OL,12,FIt was claimed that the officer was
OL,13,Ftoo ill to work for the police, but
OL,14,Fallegedly managed to do so for the new
OL,15,Flegacy body ` the Independent
OL,16,FCommission for Reconciliation and
OL,17,FInformation Recovery (ICRIR).
OL,19,FThe officer, who worked for the unit
OL,20,Fthat investigated wrongdoing within
OL,21,Fthe police, was suspended.
