OL,7,FA criminal investigation quickly
OL,8,Ffollowed, and almost three months on,
OL,9,Fthere has been an update.
OL,11,FUTV can reveal the criminal
OL,12,Finvestigation is complete and the
OL,13,Fofficer is facing possible fraud
OL,14,Fcharges.
OL,16,FHe is still suspended and on full pay
OL,17,Fpending an ongoing internal misconduct
OL,18,Finvestigation.
