OL,7,FUTV can also reveal that the PSNI
OL,8,Fsubmitted a file to the Public
OL,9,FProsecution Service on Tuesday for
OL,10,Fconsideration.
OL,12,F"A misconduct investigation is ongoing
OL,13,Fand a file was submitted to the Public
OL,14,FProsecution Service for consideration
OL,15,Fyesterday, Tuesday 27th May," the PSNI
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,18,FUTV understands the alleged offences
OL,19,Fare fraud by false representation and
OL,20,Ffraud by failing to disclose
OL,21,Finformation.
