OL,7,FWe tried to contact the officer at the
OL,8,Fcentre of this investigation but did
OL,9,Fnot receive a response.
OL,11,FThe legacy body, the ICRIR, said it
OL,12,Fdoes not comment on employment issues.
OL,14,FThe case has been raised privately
OL,15,Fwith police chiefs and policing board
OL,16,Fmember Nuala McAllister who said she
OL,17,Fhoped the internal investigation will
OL,18,Fnot be a lengthy process.
