OL,7,F"One thing that particularly
OL,8,Fdisappoints me is the length of time
OL,9,Fit actually takes to go through these
OL,10,Fmisconduct cases," she said.
OL,12,F"I'll hopefully be bringing forward
OL,13,Fsome amendments to the justice bill
OL,14,Fthat actually deal with a number of
OL,15,Fissues. However, in this particular
OL,16,Fissue, it is quite frankly
OL,17,Fembarrassing for the PSNI."
